David Eldon Hardy



Mr. David E. Hardy is Secretary, Vice President-Legal & General Counsel at Gran Tierra Energy, Inc., a Member at Law Society of Alberta, a Member at The Association of International Petroleum Negotiators, and Secretary at Gran Tierra Exchangeco, Inc.
He received his graduate degree from the University of Calgary.



